<plot>A cinematic parable that takes place in two time zones. A Jewish couple - on the run from the Nazis in 1938 - suddenly find themselves in a desolate world where history and memory have been outlawed. Their struggle is to preserve their love and their culture in this strange and anonymous place - by invoking the terrifying power of memory.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?268007</url></doc>
